graph LR
    classDef primary fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef subagent fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100,stroke-width:1px
    classDef human fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    classDef skill fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray:5 5
    classDef artifact fill:#eeeeee,stroke:#616161,stroke-width:1px

    H[Human]:::human
    BS["@specrepo-bootstrapper"]:::primary
    RA["@request-author"]:::primary
    SR["@spec-reviewer"]:::subagent
    AA["@architecture-approver"]:::subagent
    SC["@spec-coder"]:::primary
    IR["@implementation-reviewer"]:::subagent
    TR["@test-reviewer"]:::subagent

    ReqSkill["specrepo-request"]:::skill
    PropSkill["specrepo-proposal"]:::skill
    ApprovalSkill["specrepo-approval"]:::skill
    ImplReviewSkill["specrepo-implementation-review"]:::skill
    VerifySkill["specrepo-verification"]:::skill
    CommitSkill["specrepo-autocommit"]:::skill

    H -->|calls once| BS
    H -->|calls| RA
    H -->|after approval| SC

    RA -->|loads| ReqSkill
    RA -->|delegates| SR
    SR -->|loads| PropSkill
    SR -->|delegates| AA
    AA -->|loads| ApprovalSkill
    AA -->|returns recommendation| H

    SC -->|delegates if missing review| IR
    IR -->|loads| ImplReviewSkill
    IR -->|returns proceed / stop| SC
    SC -->|loads| VerifySkill
    SC -->|delegates after verification| TR
    TR -->|loads| VerifySkill
    TR -->|returns pass / needs more tests / blocked| SC
    SC -->|loads after pass| CommitSkill

    BS -.->|creates / updates| Agents[AGENTS.md]:::artifact
    BS -.->|creates| SpecRepo[specrepo docs/templates/specs]:::artifact
    RA -.->|creates| Request[Request file]:::artifact
    SR -.->|creates| Proposal[Architecture proposal]:::artifact
    AA -.->|creates on approve| Approval[Approval record]:::artifact
    IR -.->|creates| ImplReview[Implementation review]:::artifact
    SC -.->|changes| Code[Code + tests + docs + specs]:::artifact
    TR -.->|reviews| Evidence[Test and verification evidence]:::artifact

    subgraph Config[opencode.jsonc]
        SkillPerms[Per-agent skill permissions]:::skill
        TaskPerms[Per-agent task permissions]:::skill
    end

    SkillPerms -.-> RA
    SkillPerms -.-> SR
    SkillPerms -.-> AA
    SkillPerms -.-> IR
    SkillPerms -.-> SC
    SkillPerms -.-> TR
    TaskPerms -.-> RA
    TaskPerms -.-> SR
    TaskPerms -.-> SC
